column4: This is the configured voltage setting.  If there is only one voltage setting the usage must be implemented with that one choice.  When this usage (*.OutputSystem.VoltageACSetting_BF) is written the microlink master will transmit row 0  immediately after echoing the write.  This is done so transfer points and other settings can have their limits re-described.
